Package uk.ac.hope.csc.hostel.management.system

Class HManagementSystem

java.lang.Object
uk.ac.hope.csc.hostel.management.system.HManagementSystem
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class HManagementSystem extends Object implements Serializable
This class represents the 'entry point' for the HManagementSystem. Use this class to get back lists of rooms, students and to add delete a student from a room etc...
